### 🌐 Live Website: [smart-spam-detector.streamlit.app](https://smart-spam-detector.streamlit.app/)

[smart-spam-detector.streamlit.app](https://smart-spam-detector.streamlit.app/)
A machine learning-powered web application that classifies messages as Spam or Ham (Not Spam). This project uses a Multinomial Naive Bayes model with TF-IDF vectorization.

## 🚀 Features
- Modern UI: Built with Streamlit for a clean and interactive user experience.
- Efficient Processing: Implements text preprocessing (tokenization, stopword removal, stemming).
- Real-time Prediction: Instantly classifies entered text.

## 🛠️ Tech Stack
- Frontend: Streamlit
- Machine Learning: Scikit-Learn
- Natural Language Processing: NLTK
- Data Handling: Pandas, Numpy

