## 🧠 Model Training
If you want to retrain the model:

```
python3 train.py
```

This will download the dataset and regenerate model.pkl and vectorizer.pkl.

```
model.pkl
```


```
vectorizer.pkl
```

## 📜 Dataset
The model is trained on the [UCI SMS Spam Collection Dataset](https://www.kaggle.com/datasets/uciml/sms-spam-collection-dataset).

